# Revolutionizing Liver Care: Predicting Liver Cirrhosis using ML

This project aims to develop a predictive model for early detection of liver cirrhosis using advanced machine learning techniques. It demonstrates the potential of AI to support early diagnosis and optimize healthcare resources.

## üîç Features
- Predict liver cirrhosis risk from patient data
- User-friendly Flask web interface
- ML model trained using Random Forest with 68% accuracy
- Integrated with Normalizer and saved models

## üß† Technologies Used
- Python, Pandas, Scikit-learn, Matplotlib
- Flask (Web Framework)
- HTML/CSS/JavaScript for UI
- Jupyter Notebook for model training


